    Basics

    Get SWLI estimates and uncertainty

    swli_results.Rd

    Get SWLI estimates and uncertainty

    Usage

    swli_results(obj)

    Arguments

    obj

    An object of class BTFr from run_core

    Value

    Table of results and plot

    Examples

    # \donttest{
test_modern_mod <- run_modern(
  modern_elevation = NJ_modern_elevation,
  modern_species = NJ_modern_species,
  n.iter = 10,
  n.burnin = 1,
  n.thin = 1
)
